  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The purpose of this project is to promote early case detection of leprosy and LF among women and children, to prevent disability and halt the worsening of existing disability among people affected by neglected diseases. The focus is also to empower the people affected to claim their rights. Along the way we also aim to reduce stigma and discrimination.</narrative>
